title: Indonesia GDP From Services
description: GDP from Services in Indonesia increased to 53449.60 IDR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 from 53355.70 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Services in Indonesia averaged 39484.07 IDR Billion from 2010 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 53578.40 IDR Billion in the fourth quarter of 2019 and a record low of 23736.80 IDR Billion in the first quarter of 2010. This page provides the latest reported value for - Indonesia Gdp From Services - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Statistics Indonesia
